{"TopicId":177437,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"The bug of amazing indestructibility!","CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-09T11:30:35Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-09T11:30:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t know how the heck I managed this one, but I seem to have found a bug that renders my plane virtually indestructible.\u00A0 Some combination of BD Armory, Camera Tools and Mission Builder gives your plane super powers.\u00A0 The odd thing is, other planes crashed and were destroyed, but this one and one other just wouldn\u0027t die.\u00A0 I noticed it while it was on autopilot; I took it off auto and proceeded to bash it into the ground a few times with no damage.\u00A0 Check out the video. It\u0027s about 2 minutes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/aVSxD43R7ao?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-08-09T18:43:42Z\u0022 title=\u002208/09/2018 06:43  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 9, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Klapaucius\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Egrammar, clarity\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"swjr-swis","CreatedById":152460,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-09T13:24:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhite-haired old knight, after observing the effect of your mod selection: \u0022You chose... wisely.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DoctorDavinci","CreatedById":150019,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-09T15:02:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/181256-klapaucius/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022181256\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/181256-klapaucius/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Klapaucius\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0- could you run some more tests with the MH expansion installed .... My spidey senses are tingling and I have a suspicion that the MH DLC is messing with BDAc\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI personally dont have MH so am unable to test any of my suspicions (I\u0027m a cheap stand-up guy ... prefer to make my own mission builder\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnyways, if you are so inclined it would be an immeasurable help\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-09T18:11:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223430666\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022177437\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221533826956\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150019\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DoctorDavinci\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, DoctorDavinci said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/181256-klapaucius/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022181256\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/181256-klapaucius/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Klapaucius\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0- could you run some more tests with the MH expansion installed .... My spidey senses are tingling and I have a suspicion that the MH DLC is messing with BDAc\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI personally dont have MH so am unable to test any of my suspicions (I\u0027m a cheap stand-up guy ... prefer to make my own mission builder\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnyways, if you are so inclined it would be an immeasurable help\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can, but it may be at least a week. Last night was an indulged interlude (as is posting this morning). Due to outside commitments, I need to take a break from KSP for a bit, so I might not be able to devote the time right away.\u00A0 My hunch, however, is that I reset the minimum altitude to 150 meters on a couple of the planes,. However, since I was in the mountains, the ground is higher\u00A0than that. I wonder if it is getting confused over relative vs absolute altitude and not realizing it has hit the ground?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo be honest, I am rather enjoying this bug\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nAs for Mission Builder--$15 for the flexibility it gives you.... I never make missions, I use it as a hyper-edit with lots of extra flexibility built in.\u00A0It would have taken me ages to set these up, and I have found I really enjoy setting up scenarios for\u00A0good photos and video.\u00A0 It is, however still buggy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0As you can see, BD Armory\u00A0works brilliantly with hydrofoils as well \u003Cspan\u003E:\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u00225W6MP6k.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/5W6MP6k.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00222cPZE8T.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/2cPZE8T.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022SPXm9Ur.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/SPXm9Ur.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022wvOenCr.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/wvOenCr.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022rFg1fOv.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/rFg1fOv.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Lx5jvXJ.png\u0022 class=\u